title: Starts of the Week + Week 9 Breakdown, Boom Boom! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/3
description:
Week 9 is here! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Starts of the Week and lots of Week 9 matchup previews! Plus, injury updates, a new edition of “Never Not Working,” and the Boom Boom Kicker! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 3rd, 2022.
